description: Join  Burger-Lenehan and Cecily Kellogg, Seema Thomas, and Katy Thorbahn as they lead you through a self-assessment of your skill sets, abilities, how you like to work, what you have to offer, assets, and experiences. We hope you will leave refreshed and renewed!
title: WITS PHLPreview: Shifting Careers: Changing Gears or Changing Lanes
